    {
      "chinese": "這兩塊居住地區的水源和空氣到目前還没有被污染。這裡休閒農業區最適合栽培有機農業，無農藥和化學肥料，完全依靠土壤的地力栽培作物，並採用祖先慣用的自然農業栽培法。因此，設置休閒農業應列為部落的重點計畫之一。",
      "ab": "Ona kaitiraan a tosa pala, caay ho ka mapakadit ko nanom ato fali ira. O satatodongay a pipaloma to masa’Amisay a pikaomah, awaay ko sawalak ato sapa’iyo, saheto o sera ko piarawan a mikaomah to mipaloma maemin, mitodong to no kalitengan ho a pakomira hanay ko pipalahad. Maan sa, mipatireng kita to halaka no niyaro’ay i, o samakenaay a halaka no niyaro’, mipatireng to haholohololan a omah.",
      "order": "2",
      "sound": "https://dzywvpqnys6mw.cloudfront.net/files/2021/01/26/3f829e4bbf06ef5c7e66fb23666e44a5.wav",
